title: Rebel Diaz discography (m4a, mp3)
description:
Rebel Diaz is a political hip hop trio out of the Bronx, New York and Chicago, IL consisting of Rodrigo Venegas (RodStarz) Gonzalo Venegas (G1), Julio Calderon (DJ Illanoiz), and formerly Lah Tere.

These guys do really great stuff with the money they make from their music and merchandise (hint hint) and are absolutely committed to effecting mass political and social change through art and activism.
